              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/15 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-white text-lg leading-tight">Cookloop</div>
                  <div class="text-emerald-400 text-xs font-medium">KI-Essensplanung</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
                Live
              </span>
            </div>

            <!-- Tagline -->
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-3 leading-snug">Weniger wegwerfen. Besser planen. KI kocht mit.</p>

            <!-- Description -->
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5 flex-1">
              Cookloop erstellt Wochenspeisepläne, die Zutaten intelligent weiterverwenden. So landet weniger im Müll. Claude generiert im Hintergrund, die Nutzerpräferenzen bestimmen das Ergebnis. Nachhaltigkeit nicht als Motto, sondern als Funktion.
            </p>

            <!-- Professional relevance note -->
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 p-3 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/8 border border-emerald-500/15 mb-5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300/80 leading-relaxed">KI von Grund auf selbst integriert. Mit eigenen Entscheidungen darüber, wo sie wirklich hilft und wo nicht.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Stack + Link -->
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 flex-wrap">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                {['Next.js', 'Claude API', 'Supabase', 'Stripe', 'TypeScript'].map(t => (
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white/5 text-gray-400 border border-white/8 rounded-md">{t}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <a href="https://cookloop.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
                App öffnen
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DartsIQ -->
        <div class="group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-950/20 to-[#080B14]">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
          <div class="relative p-7 flex flex-col h-full">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-5">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/15 border border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-red-400 flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-bold text-white text-lg leading-tight">DartsIQ</div>
                  <div class="text-red-400 text-xs font-medium">Darts Training & Analytics</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
                Live MVP
              </span>
            </div>

            <!-- Tagline -->
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-white mb-3 leading-snug">Wer die Doppel trifft, gewinnt. DartsIQ zeigt dir, warum du sie verpasst.</p>

            <!-- Description -->
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5 flex-1">
              Ein vollständiges SaaS-Produkt mit Heatmap-Analyse für Checkout-Quoten, sechs Trainingsspielen, Turnierverwaltung und KI-gestützter Spielauswertung. Freemium-Modell mit Stripe. Alles selbst entwickelt.
            </p>

            <!-- Professional relevance note -->
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5 p-3 rounded-xl bg-red-500/8 border border-red-500/15 mb-5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-300/80 leading-relaxed">Datenmodellierung, Analytics und Produktentscheidungen. Praxisnah erprobt, nicht nur theoretisch.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Stack + Link -->
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 flex-wrap">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                {['Next.js', 'Supabase', 'Stripe', 'Recharts', 'Vitest', 'Claude API'].map(t => (
                  <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-white/5 text-gray-400 border border-white/8 rounded-md">{t}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <a href="https://dartsiq.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
                App öffnen
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Blog -->
  {posts.length > 0 && (
    <section id="blog" class="py-28 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-16">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Blog</p>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Gedanken & Insights</h2>
          </div>
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog`} class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors font-medium group">
            Alle Artikel
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {posts.map((post) => {
            const formattedDate = new Intl.DateTimeFormat('de-DE', { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' }).format(post.data.date);
            return (
              <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog/${post.slug}`} class="group block bg-white/3 hover:bg-white/5 border border-white/8 hover:border-white/15 rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                  {post.data.tags.slice(0,2).map(tag => (
                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 text-xs text-brand-400 bg-brand-500/10 rounded-md">{tag}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors">{post.data.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2 mb-4 leading-relaxed">{post.data.description}</p>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-mono">{formattedDate}</span>
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600 group-hover:text-brand-400 transition-all group-hover:translate-x-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </a>
            );
          })}
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center sm:hidden">
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}blog`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors">
            Alle Artikel ansehen
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  )}

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section id="kontakt" class="py-28 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Kontakt</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Lass uns sprechen</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Du möchtest wissen, was KI für dein Unternehmen leisten kann? Schreib mir kurz. Ich melde mich innerhalb von 24 Stunden.
      </p>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/10 to-blue-600/5 rounded-3xl blur-xl"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white/3 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10">
          <!-- Formspree: Konto auf formspree.io erstellen, Form-ID unten eintragen -->
          <form
            action="https://formspree.io/f/xgopevdy"
            method="POST"
            class="space-y-5 text-left"
          >
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2" for="name">Name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  name="name"
                  required
                  placeholder="Max Mustermann"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 focus:border-brand-500/50 focus:bg-white/8 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-600 text-sm outline-none transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2" for="email">E-Mail</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  name="email"
                  required
                  placeholder="max@unternehmen.de"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 focus:border-brand-500/50 focus:bg-white/8 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-600 text-sm outline-none transition-all"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2" for="subject">Thema</label>
              <select
                id="subject"
                name="subject"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 focus:border-brand-500/50 rounded-xl text-white text-sm outline-none transition-all appearance-none"
              >
                <option value="" class="bg-[#0d1117]">Bitte wählen...</option>
                <option value="ki-automatisierung" class="bg-[#0d1117]">KI-Automatisierung</option>
                <option value="ki-beratung" class="bg-[#0d1117]">KI-Beratung / KI-Audit</option>
                <option value="digitale-transformation" class="bg-[#0d1117]">Digitale Transformation</option>
                <option value="sonstiges" class="bg-[#0d1117]">Sonstiges</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2" for="message">Nachricht</label>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                name="message"
                required
                rows="4"
                placeholder="Beschreib kurz dein Unternehmen und was du dir von KI erhoffst..."
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 focus:border-brand-500/50 focus:bg-white/8 rounded-xl text-white placeholder-gray-600 text-sm outline-none transition-all resize-none"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <button
              type="submit"
              class="w-full py-3.5 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-400 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/25 text-base"
            >
              Nachricht absenden
            </button>
          </form>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <span>Oder direkt via:</span>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/marlon-b-26203116a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 font-medium transition-colors">
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
